   <text>
      <front>
         <div type="tipografia" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
            <p rend="writing-mode(horizontal-lr) text-orientation(sideways)" part="N">
               <s> G. Buscaglione: Dal monte al piano 
                                   Descendant a la plame - Coming down </s>
               <s> 246 </s>
            </p>
         </div>
      </front>
      <body>
         <div type="fronte" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
            <figure>
               <head>Dal monte al piano</head>
               <figDesc> Donna discende dal monte 
               </figDesc>
            </figure>
         </div>
         <div type="retro">
            <div type="message">
               <opener>
                  <dateline/>
               </opener>
               <div type="postcard-body">
                  <p type="retro">
                     <lb/>            Carisfima, <lb/>            ricevuta tua cartolina, grazie infini - <lb/>            te. Se hai occasione di andare da <lb/>            Bertazzi dopo al 30 giugno chiedigli<lb/>            qualche cosa per <gap reason="illegible"/> perchè se <lb/>            nulla otterrò per trasferimento<lb/>            sono decisa a fare il concorso<lb/>            Quando avrò avuto questa notizia<lb/>            che tu gentilmente mi darai <lb/>            verrò a Ravenna. Di nuovo<lb/>            Grazie. Saluti a tutti per me <lb/>            e a te da tutti. <lb/>            Baci. </p>
                  <p type="fronte"/>
               </div>
               <closer>
                  <lb/>
                  <signed>
                     <persName>
                        <forename ref="Bianca">Bianca</forename>
                     </persName>
                  </signed>
               </closer>
            </div>
            <div type="address-destination">
               <p>
                  <address>
                     <addrLine>
                        <lb/>            Signorina<lb/>            Oliva Turtura <lb/>            Via Girolamo Rosfi 58 <lb/>            Ravenna</addrLine>
                  </address>
               </p>
            </div>
            <div type="postmark-postage">
               <ab/>
            </div>
            <div type="secondamano">
               <ab type="paratext">
                  <add>
                     <num type="cardinal"> 106 </num>
                  </add>
               </ab>
            </div>
         </div>
      </body>
